Third Department,

May, 1955.

(May 11, 1955.) Charles Akullian, Respondent, v. Thomas Donelian, Appellant. Thomas Donelian et al., Appellants, v. Charles Akullian, Respondent.

Motion to dismiss appeal granted, by default. Present — Poster, P. J., Coon, Halpern, Imrie and Zeller, JJ.
